---

<section class="b-problema" aria-labelledby="problema-heading">
  <div class="b-container">
    <div class="b-section-label b-reveal">El problema</div>
    <h2 class="b-problema-h2 b-reveal b-reveal-delay-1" id="problema-heading">
      Tienes la experiencia.<br />
      Falta la <span style="color:var(--red)">estrategia</span>.
    </h2>
    <div class="b-problema-grid">
      <div class="b-pain b-reveal b-reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="b-pain-n" style="color:var(--red)">01</div>
        <h3 class="b-pain-t">Envías CVs</h3>
        <p class="b-pain-d">sin recibir respuesta. El silencio se volvió regla.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="b-pain b-pain--mid b-reveal b-reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="b-pain-n">02</div>
        <h3 class="b-pain-t">No destacas</h3>
        <p class="b-pain-d">aunque tu experiencia sea sólida y completa.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="b-pain b-reveal b-reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="b-pain-n" style="color:var(--red)">03</div>
        <h3 class="b-pain-t">Estancado</h3>
        <p class="b-pain-d">sin dirección y sin conseguir entrevistas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
